name: 2ch
intro: This indicates an attempt to access 2ch.2ch is a social networking bulletin board system in Japan.

name: Dnscat2
intro: This indicates an attempt to use the Dnscat2 protocol.Dnscat2 is a protocol used to tunnel traffic over DNS, HTTP, ICMP, etc.

name: FC2
intro: This indicates an attempt to access Fc2.Fc2 is a Japanese website that provides multiple services such as blog, videos, image resize, etc. It is one of the most popular video hosting service in Japan.

name: Leaf.2
intro: This indicates an attempt to use Leaf-2 protocol.It has the ID number 26 in the IP protocol list.

name: Trunk.2
intro: This indicates an attempt to use the TRUNK-2 protocol.It has the ID number 24 in the IP protocol list.

name: ANts.P2P
intro: This indicates an attempt to access ANts P2P.ANts P2P is an anonymous peer-to-peer open source file sharing software written in Java. It provides multiple sources download, automatic resume and sources...

name: 2ch_Post
intro: This indicates an attempt to post a comment on 2ch.2ch Post detects if a user post a comment or reply on the platform.
